<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="scroll-smooth" lang="it">

<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>

<body class="bg-background-light text-slate-800 font-sans transition-colors duration-300">
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <section class="pt-32 pb-12 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-emerald-600">
          Parliamo del tuo futuro IT
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Hai un progetto in mente o hai bisogno di una consulenza specializzata? Il nostro team di esperti è pronto ad
          aiutarti a semplificare la tua infrastruttura tecnologica.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-24">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div
          class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/50 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/50 dark:shadow-none border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-8 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">send</span>
            Inviaci un messaggio
          </h2>
          <form action="#" class="space-y-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2" for="first-name">Nome</label>
                <input
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent transition-all outline-none"
                  id="first-name" placeholder="Mario" type="text" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2" for="last-name">Cognome</label>
                <input
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent transition-all outline-none"
                  id="last-name" placeholder="Rossi" type="text" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2" for="email">Email Aziendale</label>
              <input
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent transition-all outline-none"
                id="email" placeholder="m.rossi@azienda.it" type="email" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2" for="subject">Oggetto</label>
              <select
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent transition-all outline-none appearance-none"
                id="subject">
                <option>Consulenza IT</option>
                <option>Sviluppo Software</option>
                <option>Opportunità di Lavoro</option>
                <option>Altro</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2" for="message">Messaggio</label>
              <textarea
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent transition-all outline-none"
                id="message" placeholder="Come possiamo aiutarti?" rows="4"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex items-center h-5">
                <input class="h-4 w-4 text-primary focus:ring-primary border-slate-300 rounded" id="privacy"
                  name="privacy" type="checkbox" />
              </div>
              <div class="ml-3 text-sm">
                <label class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400" for="privacy">Accetto la <a
                    class="text-primary hover:underline" href="#">Privacy Policy</a> per il trattamento dei miei dati
                  personali.</label>
              </div>
            </div>
            <button
              class="w-full py-4 bg-primary hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-bold rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0"
              type="submit">
              Invia Richiesta
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div
              class="p-6 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">phone_in_talk</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg mb-1">Chiamaci</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mb-2">Lun-Ven dalle 9:00 alle 18:00</p>
              <a class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline" href="tel:+39021234567">+39 02 1234567</a>
            </div>
            <div
              class="p-6 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">mail</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg mb-1">Scrivici</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mb-2">Ti risponderemo entro 24h</p>
              <a class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline" href="mailto:info@b4us.it">info@b4us.it</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 flex-shrink-0 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">location_on</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg mb-1">La nostra sede</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Via Innovazione, 42 - 20100 Milano (MI), Italia</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="relative w-full h-[300px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-inner bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700">
              <img alt="Mappa sede B4US" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80"
                src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAPkcEMmJq4o5a36UQ8obiSKsnZ8lxRTL-3uEMcw1Fe9CXrr7KNiFDzD7cJLh2Piq_uuMX4lwC6egIQYAZf5m63LYyhhAuJr_fY-GDRvTkeVu2K9aYGGAjzkoi-qT2h2EEdXMvxKRt15uu7PfD9i0mIA2i_r5aHMxXXdE3oN6ZwN4HvrtuGwi-6qtGrqO6FPnJsGd4YLRo11n6EJ0Girt6FZ-Z4Sxs4TBIitw9-jGDb8YMnscshrQ8_QVKwlWvvir-1deHtb3f6_b9R" />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <div
                  class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl flex items-center gap-3 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 animate-bounce">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">location_on</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="font-bold">B4US IT</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-primary/5 dark:bg-primary/10 border-l-4 border-primary">
            <p class="italic text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              "Non pretendiamo che le cose cambino, se continuiamo a fare le stesse cose... La vera crisi è
              l'incompetenza. Senza crisi non ci sono sfide, senza sfide la vita è una routine, una lenta agonia."
            </p>
            <cite class="block text-right font-display font-bold text-primary">— Albert Einstein</cite>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>